# DDD Strategic Hub

High-level domain modeling and architectural mapping.

## Strategic Patterns
- Ubiquitous Language
- Bounded Contexts
- Context Mapping (ACL, OHS, Shared Kernel)

## C4 Mapping
- L1 (System Context) -> Domain
- L2 (Container) -> Bounded Context
- L3 (Component) -> Aggregates
- L4 (Code) -> Entities/VOs

## Workflows
1. Identify Domains
2. Define Bounded Contexts
3. Map to C4 Containers
4. Establish Upstream/Downstream
